@startuml seq-signin
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Times New Roman
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #000000
  ArrowFontColor #000000
  LifeLineBorderColor #333333
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantFontColor #000000
  ParticipantBorderColor #333333
  ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ActorBorderColor #333333
  DatabaseBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  DatabaseBorderColor #333333
}
actor User
participant "Web Console" as Console
participant "Backend" as Backend
database "Local Database" as DB

User -> Console : enter email and password
Console -> Backend : send sign-in request
Backend -> DB : look up user by email
DB --> Backend : stored user and hash
Backend -> Backend : check password (scrypt)
Backend --> Console : session token
Console --> User : open the dashboard
@enduml
